With the Cauterist re-firing operation disrupted, the Ember Crucible Regent, the administrative embodiment of the re-firing doctrine, has emerged to enforce its authority directly. The Regent operates as both a legal mechanism and a lethal hazard, blocking the Cinder Gate approach to the Saltglass Reach and Mafdet. The Mafdet postmaster has issued a final dismantlement writ authorizing direct action against the Regent to restore access to the eastern transit corridor.
The Ember Crucible Regent has been dismantled and the re-firing doctrine it embodied has lost its enforcing mechanism. The Mafdet postmaster has transmitted the dismantlement confirmation to the Cinder Gate jurisdiction office and forwarded the final sanction record to the Southern Oasis Casualty Ledger as documentary evidence for the territorial nullification hearing.
